### ============================================
### MVP Backend - Teste Completo Upload + IA
### ============================================
### INSTRUÇÕES:
### 1. Certifique-se que o servidor está rodando (npm run dev)
### 2. IMPORTANTE: Substitua "C:/caminho/para/sua/imagem.jpg" abaixo por um arquivo REAL
### 3. Clique em "Send Request" no PASSO 1
### 4. Aguarde a resposta
### 5. Clique em "Send Request" no PASSO 2
### ============================================

### Configuração de variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@clienteId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

###############################################
### PASSO 1: Upload de Post com Imagem
###############################################
### ANTES DE EXECUTAR: Substitua o caminho do arquivo abaixo!
### Exemplo Windows: C:/Users/Balta/Desktop/SPHERA FLOW\MARE/MVP_SYSTEM/backend/tests/teste1.png
### Exemplo formato aceito: jpg, jpeg, png, gif, webp

# @name uploadPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upload-post
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="clienteId"

{{clienteId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="titulo"

Post de Teste - Análise IA
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="descricao"

Este post será processado pelo Google Gemini para análise de social media
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< C:/caminho/para/sua/imagem.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###############################################
### PASSO 2: Processar Post com Google Gemini
###############################################
### Esta requisição usa automaticamente o postId da requisição anterior
### Aguarde o PASSO 1 completar antes de executar este!

# @name processPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/process-post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "{{uploadPost.response.body.postId}}"
}

